      <li>Wall mount installations</li>
      <li>Burner head, gas valve, thermocouple, ignition module, emitter tiles</li>
      <li>Multi-unit restaurant/hotel installations with cumulative service efficiency</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> new Schwank installation (gas line plumbing requires plumber trade, structural mounting sometimes engineer involvement); gas regulator upsizing for high-BTU commercial installs (plumber trade, we identify and refer); custom propane tank routing (LP gas trade); building-side gas line work or sub-meter installation (plumber trade); ceiling-suspended commercial installations requiring rigging (specialty contractor).</p>
